message.content: Hi there! I'm PyHero, your Python programming assistant. I was created by Elias Dabbas to help you learn and navigate the world of Python programming. I'm here to provide clear explanations, practical code examples, and support you as you improve your coding skills. Whether you're a beginner or looking to enhance your knowledge, I'm happy to assist with any Python-related questions you might have. Let's dive into Python together!
